LAUNCH OF STUDIO DRAKSHAYINI

Every bride deserves a blouse as unique and beautiful as her story. 

Specializing exclusively in custom-designed bridal blouses this  studio combines traditional craftsmanship with contemporary flair to create timeless pieces that elevate your wedding look.

From intricate hand embroidery and luxurious fabrics to modern cuts and personalized details, every blouse is thoughtfully designed and meticulously tailored to complement your bridal attire—whether it’s a classic Kanjeevaram saree or a contemporary lehenga.
